    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>None of the above methods worked for me.<br />\nWhat worked for me was simply removing all items from the cache directory in <code>/Users/&lt;username&gt;/.gradle/caches/build-cache-1/</code>.</p>\n"
  }, {
